OL,3,CMan charged with murder after
OL,4,CLichfield assault
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a man who was seriously
OL,8,Fassaulted in Lichfield died.
OL,10,FStaffordshire police were called to
OL,11,Fthe Ricco and Loren bar on Market
OL,12,FStreet at 11.25pm on Sunday 24 May
OL,13,Ffollowing reports that two men had
OL,14,Fbeen punched.
OL,16,FOne of the men, who was seriously
OL,17,Finjured, died in hospital on Tuesday
OL,18,F26 May.
OL,20,FPolice said his family are being
OL,21,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
