OL,3,CMan charged with murder after
OL,4,CLichfield assault
OL,6,FThe second victim was also taken to
OL,7,Fhospital but has since been discharged.
OL,9,F36-year-old Billy Allison, who is from
OL,10,FSolihull, was arrested just after 5am
OL,11,Fon Monday 26 May.
OL,13,FHe has been charged with murder and
OL,14,FSection 18 grievous bodily harm with
OL,15,Fintent.
OL,17,FAllison is due to appear at the North
OL,18,FStaffordshire Justice Centre on
OL,19,FWednesday 27 May.
